                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340904-84-off467 t18340904-84-cd470"></join>, I paid the prisoner 8s. 6d., and on the 19th of July, 6s. 10d., for Mrs. Fortman.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. Q. Have you any bill? A. Here is a book which I kept - I paid the prisoner myself, weekly.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340904-84-victim549" type="victimName">
